{"tid":1361174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗恐襲】Marco Rubio譴責事件 「中共利用犯罪集團襲擊示威者」","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:35:14.000Z","uid":54733,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"99364fd4abc669f90285b6498326d5c31a4686a9","tid":1361174,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190724/large/1563946102_f9b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190724%2Flarge%2F1563946102_f9b2.jpg&h=40beaabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會和行政當局中國委員會（CECC）聯合主席、共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio），周一在Twitter譴責本港元朗周日發生的襲擊事件，甚至指中共在背後策動襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧在帖文寫道：「中國共產黨利用有組織犯罪集團襲擊香港的示威者。看看我們正在與怎樣的人打交道」。他又指中國違反所有在香港回歸時作出的承諾，美國難以信賴中國會遵守現在所達成的任何協議。<br />\n<br />\n他同時上載短片說：「中國一直有系統地剝削香港的自由、民主及政制，民眾最終忍無可忍，他們開始抗議。中國政府的回應似乎是授權街頭黑幫成員，這些暴徒毒打示威者。不只是示威者，而是任何在鐵路站的人。」"},{"pid":"5cce5c0260d66eb80c0b1320a884190bd90b6d73","tid":1361174,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190724/59857502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59857502&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=23c04831\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59857502&h=1a53a181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190724/59857502</a>"},{"pid":"93b788bf5eb745027863096441684a91f514908d","tid":1361174,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1153677176513990658?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1153677176513990658%3Fs%3D19&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=4b01add1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1153677176513990658%3Fs%3D19&h=0ae608bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1153677176513990658?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"adb43a93ee12edf4daf612b4fce9d3b98f01c081","tid":1361174,"uid":216789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e871ca97abc4172017f3d6c4a3bb38f0bb2ebb7","tid":1361174,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"435e0f466f2400792f9d8e6f2f36976517469920","tid":1361174,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0609262abb760669f9012aca6c6e0076296a70","tid":1361174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"(突發) 有人邀請鄉事派參加元朗727遊行!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361593</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推同share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba32e1f0b676d793647f724d4c7d26a9be6f9ca4","tid":1361174,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"等睇口交部回應，今次事件再次升溫至全球，西環777好波。"},{"pid":"f7eaf9061782b01355b0224f96c31cc84b5ec15e","tid":1361174,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"口交部發言人強烈譴責外國勢力干預終國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\